WEBVTT

39:56.899 --> 39:58.316
Thanks a lot, Georgekutty.

39:58.941 --> 40:00.524
It's been my son's biggest dream.

40:00.983 --> 40:03.274
And I don't know anyone
in the film industry.

40:03.899 --> 40:05.399
I was just wondering what to do...

40:05.608 --> 40:07.441
when God himself
sent you my way, Georgekutty.
